                                                   KisanNetworkCodingChallenge-

Backend-node.js
Description-backened is use to create services and api.
version-v10.4.1
Framework-epressjs
Npm -6.4.1
Database-  db-Mongodb version- v3.6.5
                          Object module-mongoose
Other library- twilio for sending otp to mobiles

Commands use to install-
 sudo  npm install express-generator -g
express --view=pug backend
npm install
npm install nodemon -- save
Nodemon (use node start server)



Api-

(1)-http://localhost:3000/users/sendOtp
Description-this api
Req - {
"FirstName":"kavi",
"LastName":"pal",
"UserNumber":"84481666243"
}

